":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"東南亞產業鏈家陣唔成熟，再過幾年就完全取代大陸既世界工廠，到時連唯一最龐大既實業都支撐唔住，家陣仲要未做產業轉型，就算家陣想轉阿，但比世界圍屌你貿易，金融唔開放，我真係恭喜唒你阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea6359bd43acb24c3bba39da5d2b0c6b390435d","tid":998342,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62821be5c5e46c319e2173c62cac1405db7096c8","tid":998342,"uid":80814,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:32:26.000Z","msg":"緬甸工人工資才<span style=\"color: red;\">600元</span>，還<span style=\"color: red;\">不包吃不包住</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">社保</span>也僅有20元[/red]，東莞這邊最少也要2000多元，還要包吃包住，另外還有社保，在東莞請一個工人可以在緬甸請4到5個，而且<span style=\"color: red;\">都是年輕人</span>，20歲左右，<span style=\"color: red;\">年齡大的</span>我們<span style=\"color: red;\">都不要</span><br />\n<br />\n人力真係一啲都唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"如果無任何附加價值（知識同身份etc)<br />\n人本來就係最廉價既資源"},{"pid":"b31a4492c35bbcf695f1b19afe5316a20d5641cc","tid":998342,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"一向都係低人工/成本就去開，做左幾十年人工升/規管多就搬"},{"pid":"ed9c89f72cab8260cb56b88cfcf649ab3955c479","tid":998342,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"民工: Nous somme les dieux de Sanhe <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17434d70d56d0d5bb40fcc6927801f8b017c3402","tid":998342,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62821be5c5e46c319e2173c62cac1405db7096c8","tid":998342,"uid":80814,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:32:26.000Z","msg":"緬甸工人工資才<span style=\"color: red;\">600元</span>，還<span style=\"color: red;\">